snippet.title: Pixel Stars - New Trailer
snippet.description:
Pixel Stars v1.1 Coming soon!

Endless arcade runner where you can collect and play with lots of cool pixel characters inspired by real-life stars!

Game Features:

+ More than 150 characters to unlock!
+ 7 character collections!
+ Single tap game, play with 1 hand!
+ Cool and fun pixel art style!
+ Awesome 16-bits styled music!

Download Pixel Stars on the App Store:
https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/pixel-stars/id1367783892?mt=8

Download Pixel Stars on Google Play:
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.ogrepixel.pixelstars&hl=en_US

ogrepixel.com
